biography: Nandana is a data scientist at Censius AI. She had completed her bachelors degree from College Of Engineering, Trivandrum. She had previously worked in the e-commerce industry where she had to deal with real world problem statements including product ranking and recommendation systems. She had published a research paper in health care domain in an international journal. Currently, her research interests are aligned to the Explainable AI domain.
